rows.label: bf05150100_0010
rows.name: Well then, it's about time we get going.

rows.label: bf05150100_0030
rows.name:
You take care now.
And keep yourself out of trouble, Seiryuu!

rows.label: bf05150100_0040
rows.name:
You've got quite the needlessly sharp tongue, 
haven't you?

rows.label: bf05150100_0050
rows.name: Thank you for everything you've done for us.

rows.label: bf05150100_0060
rows.name: I don't know what happened to you, but...

rows.label: bf05150100_0070
rows.name: Don't try to shoulder everything by yourself, okay?

rows.label: bf05150100_0090
rows.name:
When you're in trouble,
let him take on your burdens.

rows.label: bf05150100_0110
rows.name: Huh? What? What are you talking about?

rows.label: bf05150100_0140
rows.name:
You just concentrate on what you're doing.
Work hard, and do your best!
